g.title: http://schema.mobivoc.org/#ParkingSpace
g.text: A parking space is a location that
is designated for parking a vehicle.
A parking space has a certain size,
is sometimes marked and can be located
at roadside or inside a parking facility.
Depending on the location of the parking
space, there can be regulations regarding
the time allowed to park and a fee
paid to use the parking space.
